businesses.name: Zero-Ten Park Cebu IT Park (formerly The Company)
businesses.description: Zero-Ten Park offers a vibrant and professional environment located in the heart of Cebu IT Park. Steps away from major tech hubs, it features high-speed internet, ergonomic seating, and collaborative meeting rooms designed for startups and freelancers.

businesses.name: enspace Cebu
businesses.location: 11th Floor, Building JM del Mar Ave
businesses.description: enspace Cebu is more than just a workspace; it's a community for creators. With flexible hot desking options and private offices, we provide the perfect balance of privacy and networking opportunities. Enjoy our free flowing coffee and modern amenities.

businesses.name: Workplace Cafe
businesses.description: The Workplace Cafe is the pioneer of co-working cafes in Cebu. We offer a cozy, coffee-shop ambiance combined with productivity-focused amenities like power outlets at every table, fiber-optic internet, and nap rooms for when you need a break.

businesses.name: Sync Work + Study Hub
businesses.location: OpenUnit 11, St. Patrick's Square, R Aboitiz St.
businesses.description: Sync is designed for intense focus. Whether you are a student preparing for boards or a professional meeting a deadline, our quiet zones and study cubicles provide the distraction-free environment you need to succeed.

businesses.name: Third Wave Coffee Cebu - Bloq Cafe
businesses.location: Open2nd Floor, inside Bloq Residences Showroom, GND Arcade, F. Cabahug St.
businesses.description: Experience the art of coffee while you work. Third Wave Coffee Cebu offers a relaxed, artistic atmosphere perfect for creative work. Enjoy our specialty brews and comfortable seating in a hidden gem location.

businesses.name: Green Farm
businesses.description: Green Farm is an eco-conscious co-working space that brings nature indoors. Surrounded by plants and natural light, it is a refreshing alternative to traditional offices, promoting well-being and productivity.
